r />\n其實呢8個月以黎，乜香港人真係付出得好少咩？<br />\n有冇諗過係大佬太難打？大家已經付出左好多？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:34:47.000Z","msg":"真 每次講罷工就問 你呢"},{"pid":"fc56b8a2f2450da0b6b4109d7a51689e1f2b5edf","tid":1869014,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6198f826b7d4528dd94487e597d105ba4af0b99","tid":1869014,"uid":20809,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T02:40:30.000Z","msg":"醫護唔撚恨你句鼓勵說話，只係要你罷工<br />\n<br />\n你肯罷工話知你即場屌鳩佢，起碼你肯做<br />\n<br />\n個個淨係識&quot;醫護加油&quot;&quot;支持醫護&quot;然後繼續返工，嘔唔嘔心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:52:05.000Z","msg":"係 但兩者無衝突"},{"pid":"4e0652c109282709a86fd5daef86cb30efe26737","tid":1869014,"uid":254246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:54:51.000Z","msg":"push   多謝醫護"},{"pid":"a271431894d2a3d65402d85c61ef78be9d17095f","tid":1869014,"uid":43663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:57:21.000Z","msg":"推 講得好岩 連登上面9成都係冷嘲熱諷同嘈交 鼓勵或者建設性既野好快沉"},{"pid":"c664ecd7c283872178f9b998131f04a43b3b855e","tid":1869014,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6198f826b7d4528dd94487e597d105ba4af0b99","tid":1869014,"uid":20809,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T02:40:30.000Z","msg":"醫護唔撚恨你句鼓勵說話，只係要你罷工<br />\n<br />\n你肯罷工話知你即場屌鳩佢，起碼你肯做<br />\n<br />\n個個淨係識&quot;醫護加油&quot;&quot;支持醫護&quot;然後繼續返工，嘔唔嘔心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f436c88483e7c985119424e188ca26e6b3e0990d","tid":1869014,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2365d96506de81928e4b406a4a01aa96e96918c5","tid":1869014,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f436c